@page "/"

@* Flu Awareness Hub Home Page *@

<PageTitle>Flu Awareness Hub</PageTitle>

<div class="container-fluid text-center">
    <header class="p-5" style="background-color: #4A90E2; color: white;">
        <h1>Welcome to the Flu Fighters Denison!</h1>
        <p>Your go-to place for learning about the flu and staying healthy.</p>
    </header>

    <section class="p-5" style="background-color: #F9F9F9;">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4 p-4">
                <div class="card shadow" style="border-left: 8px solid #FF6F61;">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h2 class="card-title" style="color: #FF6F61;">What is the Flu?</h2>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            The flu (influenza) is a contagious illness that affects the respiratory system. Learn how it spreads and what symptoms to watch out for.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 p-4">
                <div class="card shadow" style="border-left: 8px solid #28B463;">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h2 class="card-title" style="color: #28B463;">Flu Prevention</h2>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            Stay safe and healthy! Discover tips on how to prevent the flu with simple steps, from hygiene practices to vaccinations.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 p-4">
                <div class="card shadow" style="border-left: 8px solid #F4D03F;">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h2 class="card-title" style="color: #F4D03F;">Symptoms to Watch</h2>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            Know the signs! From fever to fatigue, learn about common flu symptoms so you can take action quickly if you get sick.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="p-5" style="background-color: #E8F8F5;">
        <h2 style="color: #1ABC9C;">How Does the Flu Spread?</h2>
        <p>
            The flu spreads through droplets when an infected person coughs, sneezes, or talks. It can also spread by touching contaminated surfaces.
            Protect yourself by washing hands frequently, wearing masks in crowded places, and staying home when feeling unwell.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="p-5" style="background-color: #FCE5CD;">
        <h2 style="color: #E67E22;">Flu Quiz</h2>
        <p>
            Think you know everything about the flu? Test your knowledge with a fun quiz! See how well you understand prevention, symptoms, and how the flu spreads.
        </p>
    </section>

    <footer class="bg-dark text-white text-center p-3 mt-5">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Flu Fighters Denison. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</div>
